-loss-4738926%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJustifies%20Autocratic%2C%20Arrogant...%26quot%3B%3A%20M%20Kharge%20Replies%20To%20Veep's%20Letter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20has%20%26quot%3Bweaponised%26quot%3B%20the%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20as%20a%20convenient%20tool%20to%20%26quot%3Bundermine%20democracy%2C%20sabotage%20Parliamentary%20practices%20and%20throttle%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%20to%20a%20letter%20written%20by%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20the%20Chairman's%20letter%20%26quot%3Bunfortunately%20justifies%20the%20autocratic%20and%20arrogant%20attitude%20of%20the%20Government%20towards%20Parliament.%26quot%3B%20Replying%20to%20the%20points%20raised%20by%20Mr%20Dhankhar%2C%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20urged%20him%20to%20examine%20his%20concerns%20%26quot%3Bobjectively%20and%20with%20neutrality%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anything%20privilege%20motions%20have%20also%20been%20weaponised%20to%20muzzle%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20This%20is%20a%20deliberate%20design%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20to%20undermine%20Parliament%20itself.%20By%20suspending%20MPs%2C%20the%20government%20is%20effectively%20silencing%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20voters%20of%20146%20MPs%20altogether%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20also%20mentioned%20that%20disorder%20was%20deliberate%20and%20strategised%20and%20predetermined.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20submit%20that%20if%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20from%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20predetermined%20and%20premeditated%20by%20the%20Government%20and%20I%20am%20most%20sorry%20to%20say%2C%20executed%20without%20any%20application%20of%20mind%2C%20as%20can%20be%20seen%20by%20the%20suspension%20of%20an%20INDIA%20party%20MP%20who%20was%20not%20even%20present%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Dhankhar%2C%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20had%20said%20that%20his%20attempts%20to%20meet%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20were%20turned%20down%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20had%20sought%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20the%20security%20breach%20on%20December%2014%2C%20before%20the%20suspensions%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recognise%20it%20is%20well%20within%20your%20powers%20as%20Chairman%20to%20decide%20on%20these%20notices.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20regrettable%20that%20the%20Chair%20condoned%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20Government%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20even%20more%20regrettable%20that%20the%20Hon'ble%20Home%20Minister%20made%20his%20first%20public%20statement%20before%20a%20TV%20channel%20when%20Parliament%20was%20in%20session%20and%20the%20Chair%20did%20not%20find%20that%20sacrileging%20the%20temple%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20Union%20minister%20allegedly%20informed%20an%20opposition%20parliamentarian%20that%20most%20opposition%20MPs%20will%20be%20suspended%20before%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20present%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20have%20expected%20the%20Chairman%20to%20have%20inquired%20if%20such%20a%20threat%20was%20indeed%20issued.%20Such%20comments%20grossly%20undermines%20the%20Chair%20who%20we%20believe%20is%20the%20final%20authority%20on%20conducting%20the%20House%20including%20suspension%20of%20members%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20by%20suspending%20the%20MPs%2C%20the%20government%20is%20effectively%20silencing%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20voters%20of%20146%20MPs%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%C2%A0Kharge%20said%20as%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20House%2C%20the%20Chairman%20should%20protect%20the%20people's%20right%20to%20hold%20its%20government%20accountable%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chairman%20should%20also%20kindly%20note%20that%20the%20government%20has%20escaped%20accountability%20on%20all%20crucial%20issues%20like%20serious%20border%20incursions%20by%20China%2C%20or%20continued%20unrest%20in%20Manipur%20or%20the%20recent%20intrusion%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20visitors%20who%20had%20been%20facilitated%20entry%20by%20a%20BJP%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20distressing%20when%20history%20judges%20the%20presiding%20officers%20harshly%20for%20Bills%20passed%20without%20debate%20and%20not%20seeking%20accountability%20from%20the%20government.%20It%20is%20disappointing%20that%20the%20Hon'ble%20Chairman%20feels%20effecting%20suspensions%20facilitated%20legislative%20business%20by%20passing%20bills%20without%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20added%20that%20he%20is%20in%20agreement%20with%20the%20Chairman%20that%20they%20need%20to%20move%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20stressed%20that%20the%20answer%20may%20not%20lie%20in%20a%20discussion%20in%20the%20Chairman's%20chambers%2C%20if%20the%20government%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20running%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20is%20currently%20out%20of%20Delhi%20and%20it%20would%20be%20his%20%26quot%3Bprivilege%20and%20duty%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20the%20Chairman%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20is%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703496420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F3jpvv2to_mallikarjun-kharge-pti_625x300_28_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustifies-autocrat