or%20discussing%20and%20reviewing%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20set%20up%20their%20coffee%20brand%20in%202018%2C%20also%20predating%20Chamberlain's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20beans%20would%20be%20my%20fourth%20to%20try.%20But%20it%20was%20around%20this%20time%20in%20my%20coffee%20review%20week%20that%20I%20realized%20something.%20Three%20out%20of%20four%20of%20the%20bags%20I'd%20ordered%20came%20from%20Lincoln%2C%20Nebraska.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20never%20thought%20of%20the%20region%20as%20a%20coffee%20hotspot%2C%20so%20I%20looked%20deeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20out%20that%20there's%20a%20coffee%20company%20based%20there%20that%20works%20with%20online%20creators%20to%20help%20them%20create%20their%20own%20coffee%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20called%20Akira%20Coffee%20Co%20and%20it%20lists%20Top%20of%20the%20Mornin'%2C%20Florida%20Man%20Coffee%2C%20Dodger%20Coffee%20Co%2C%20and%20Carlin%20Brothers%20Coffee%20as%20its%20partners%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20I%20couldn't%20really%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20my%20third%20cup%2C%20which%20was%20made%20from%20Dodger%20Coffee%20beans%2C%20and%20my%20fourth%2C%20which%20was%20brewed%20with%20Carlin%20Brothers%20Coffee%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beans%20look%20different%20so%20they%20haven't%20just%20slapped%20different%20branding%20onto%20two%20identical%20products.%20But%20seeing%20as%20they%20are%20both%20sourced%20from%20the%20same%20place%20by%20the%20same%20company%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20they%20would%20taste%20pretty%20similar.%20They%20even%20cost%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20the%20coffee%20tasted%20good.%20It%20was%20strong%2C%20but%20not%20overly%20so.%20The%20beans%20seemed%20slightly%20sweeter%20than%20Dodger%20Coffee%20Co's%2C%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20citrus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20probably%20wouldn't%20buy%20it%20again%2C%20mainly%20because%20I%20have%20a%20surplus%20of%20beans%20now%2C%20and%20I%20slightly%20preferred%20Dodger%20Coffee%20Co.%20But%20it%20isn't%20a%20bad%20product%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%3A%20%C2%A315%20(19)%20per%20bag%2C%20%C2%A326%20(%2432)%20with%20shipping.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERating%3A%203.1%2F5%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20verdict%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20YouTuber%20coffees%20I%20drank%20were%20the%20best%20I'd%20ever%20had.%20They%20were%20all%20decent%20enough%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20none%20of%20the%20beans%20will%20go%20to%20waste%20in%20my%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20judging%20by%20the%20similarity%20of%20some%20of%20the%20products%2C%20and%20the%20more%20memorable%20flavors%20of%20others%2C%20my%20winner%20has%20to%20be%20Chamberlain%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stood%20out%20as%20an%20original%20product%20in%20a%20crowded%20field%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20companies%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing.%20It%20was%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20Chamberlain%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20into%20creating%20the%20company%2C%20rather%20than%20outsourcing%20the%20process%20to%20a%20wholesaler%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20pays%20off%20in%20the%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20came%20out%20the%20cheapest%2C%20probably%20because%20the%20company%20has%20a%20European%20warehouse%20in%20Denmark%20so%20it%20had%20less%20far%20to%20travel.%20And%20it%20was%20the%20first%20to%20arrive%2C%20which%20was%20nice%20even%20though%20it%20didn't%20majorly%20sway%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20fans%20of%20influencers%2C%20a%20bag%20of%20coffee%20beans%20is%20a%20nice%20gift.%20And%20if%20they%20are%20all%20up%20to%20the%20standard%20of%20the%20ones%20I%20tried%2C%20it%20probably%20won't%20be%20one%20that%20ends%20up%20in%20the%20trash%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-among-youtuber-coffee-brands-there-is-a-totally-clear-winner-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%