ave%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20wrestling%20and%20have%20to%20look%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20that%20are%20approaching.%20Whatever%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20new%20federation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20sport%20now.%20I%20have%20other%20responsibilities%20to%20focus%20now.%20I%20will%20be%20away%20from%20the%20politics%20of%20this%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fsanjay-singh-not-my-relative-says-brij-bhushan-on-suspension-of-wfi-backs-announcement-of-u-15-u-20-nationals-2823897%5C%22%3Ewrites%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20would%20suggest%20he%20has%20just%20being%20taken%20off%20from%20wrestling%2C%20as%20the%20public%20attention%20as%20well%20as%20visible%20annoyance%20of%20the%20influential%20Jat%20community%20in%20Haryana%20was%20getting%20hard%20to%20avoid.%20But%20B.B.S.%20Singh%20remains%20central%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20plans%20in%20the%20future%20and%20it%20has%20not%20been%20ruled%20out%20by%20the%20party%20that%20he%20may%20be%20accommodated%20in%20a%20more%20powerful%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20previously%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20(directly%20under%20the%20control%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah)%20has%20never%20really%20moved%20on%20Singh%3B%20it%20took%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20to%20even%20get%20an%20FIR%20filed.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20told%20a%20court%20in%20September%20that%20the%20BJP%20MP%20had%20%E2%80%9Coutraged%20the%20modesty%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20women%20wrestlers.%20This%20was%20when%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20was%20hearing%20the%20case%20on%20framing%20of%20charges%20against%20him%20after%20the%C2%A0chargesheet%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20case%C2%A0filed%20by%20six%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw%2Fstory%2Fbrij-bhushan-singh-harassed-wrestlers-at-every-opportunity-delhi-police-to-court-2439705-2023-09-24%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Atul%20Srivastava%2C%20representing%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20WFI%20chief%20%E2%80%9Cknew%20what%20he%20was%20doing%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20intention%20was%20to%20outrage%20the%20modesty%20of%20the%20wrestlers.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20are%20three%20types%20of%20evidence%20against%20Singh%20which%20are%20enough%20to%20frame%20charges.%20These%20include%20a%20written%20complaint%20and%20two%20recorded%20statements%20under%20Sections%20161%20(examination%20of%20witnesses%20by%20the%20police)%20and%20164%20(statements%20recorded%20by%20a%20magistrate)%20under%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC).%20Srivastava%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20the%20court%20is%20within%20its%20jurisdiction%20to%20frame%20charges%20against%20Singh.%20He%20also%20countered%20the%20argument%20made%20by%20the%20WFI%20chief%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20that%20sanction%20under%20Section%20188%20of%20the%20CrPC%20is%20required%20for%20cases%20that%20took%20place%20outside%20India.%20But%20Singh%20continued%20to%20show%20growing%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20meritorious%20students%20in%20his%20constituency%20of%20Gonda%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20how%20he%20had%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fdabang-since-childhood-failed-twice-in-class-8-says-brijbhushan-sharan-singh-while-felicitating-meritorious-students-2776476%5C%22%3Ethat%20he%20had%20been%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edabang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(muscleman)%20since%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20he%20had%2C%20after%20failing%20twice%20in%20the%208th%20standard%2C%20one%20of%20his%20classmates%20write%20his%20answer%20sheets%20by%20threatening%20to%20%E2%80%98break%E2%80%99%20his%20bones%20if%20he%20(the%20classmate)%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20election%20of%20the%20new%20president%2C%20scenes%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Fdabdaba-tha-dabdaba-rahega-says-brij-bhushan-singh-after-close-aide-wins-wfi-poll-1503251972.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edab%20daba%20thaa%2C%20dab%20daba%20rahega%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(we%20have%20had%20control%2C%20will%20retain%20control)%E2%80%9D%20emerged%2C%20with%20Singh%20being%20garlanded%20and%20feted%20%E2%80%93%20making%20clear%20there%20was%20no%20real%20change%20of%20guard.%20Medallist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20retired%20from%20wrestling%2C%20gold%20medallist%20Bajrang%20Punia%20said%20he%20was%20returning%20his%20Padmashree.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20that%2C%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20camp%20in%20Gonda%20(an%20area%20meant%20to%20be%20close%20to%20where%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20personal%20area%20of%20control%20and%20influence%20is)%20that%20the%20sports%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20Gonda%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20was%20only%20after%20his%20candidate%20(by%20his%20own%20admission)%20declared%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20new%20WFI%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20camp%20in%20Gonda%20(Singh%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency)%20that%20the%20sports%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrestlers%20were%20beaten%20up%20and%20dragged%20off%20protesting%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20of%20parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fb_bhushansharan%2Fstatus%2F1704504136299954381%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eon%20September%2020.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Singh%20sat%20and%20participated%20in%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20provides%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20and%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsexual-harassment-bjp-brij-bhushan-singh-womens-reservation-bill%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CSingh%20was%20seen%20sitting%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20among%20BJP%20MPs%20only%20a%20few%20rows%20behind%20Union%20ministers%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20as%20the%20latter%20gave%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20Bill%20and%20pledged%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20support%20towards%20women%20empowerment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703488486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25124341%2FGA1OyoaXkAIKcph.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhas-bjp-mp-ex-wfi-head-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-been-brought-down-a-peg-or-two%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20short%20answer%3A%20No.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20has%20he%20in%20fact%20been%20upgraded%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhas-bjp-mp-ex-wfi-head-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-been-brought-down-a-peg-or-two%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BTS's%20Jimin%20achieves%20historic%20milestone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703488372000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106264240%2Cimgsize-18206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbtss-jimin-achieves-historic-milestone-first-soloist-worldwide-to-secure-7-songs-with-100-no-1s-each-on-itunes-charts%2Farticleshow%2F106264280.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106264280.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3