ial-deaths-3-senior-officers-shifted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20AI%20may%20end%20up%20being%20a%20'threat'%20to%20these%20Google%20employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703485218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106263234%2Cimgsize-109532.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-ai-may-end-up-being-a-threat-to-these-google-employees%2Farticleshow%2F106263234.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20is%20reportedly%20considering%20a%20significant%20restructuring%20that%20could%20impact%20up%20to%2030%2C000%20employees%20in%20its%20ad%20sales%20team.%20The%20company%20aims%20to%20automate%20ad%20sales%20operations%20using%20AI-powered%20tools%20like%20Performance%20Max%2C%20which%20has%20become%20increasingly%20sophisticated.%20While%20job%20cuts%20are%20not%20currently%20planned%2C%20employees%20may%20be%20integrated%20into%20other%20teams.%20The%20potential%20layoffs%20would%20affect%20various%20roles%2C%20including%20account%20managers%20and%20campaign%20specialists.%20Google's%20push%20for%20AI%20is%20driven%20by%20competition%20in%20the%20advertising%20landscape%2C%20but%20critics%20raise%20concerns%20about%20impersonalisation%20and%20algorithmic%20bias.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-ai-may-end-up-being-a-threat-to-these-google-employees%2Farticleshow%2F106263234.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20The%20Year%20India%20Engaged%20The%20World%20On%20Its%20Own%20Terms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20year%202023%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20global%20order%20that%20has%20been%20fundamentally%20reconfigured%20-%20politically%2C%20economically%20and%20diplomatically.%20Trends%20that%20were%20simmering%20below%20the%20surface%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%20have%20burst%20into%20the%20open%2C%20revealing%20in%20the%20all%20their%20complexities%20the%20challenges%20that%20are%20becoming%20difficult%20to%20manage%20by%20extant%20frameworks%20and%20institutions.%20There%20is%20an%20intellectual%20void%20at%20the%20very%20heart%20of%20international%20relations%20and%20it%20is%20being%20filled%20by%20the%20overuse%20of%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bdisruption.%26quot%3B%20Whatever%20the%20world%20can't%20seem%20to%20grapple%20with%20or%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20is%20being%20labelled%20%26quot%3Bdisruptive.%26quot%3B%20Indeed%2C%20this%20is%20an%20inflection%20point%20but%20the%20underlying%20forces%20shaping%20it%20had%20been%20there%20with%20us%20for%20some%20time%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20grappling%20with%20the%20fundamental%20transformations%20brought%20in%20by%20shifting%20power%20balance%2C%20technological%20overreach%2C%20and%20institutional%20decay.%20These%20underlying%20shifts%20have%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20wars%20in%20Eurasia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20resulting%20in%20global%20inflationary%20pressures%2C%20food%20and%20energy%20crises%2C%20and%20widespread%20economic%20downturn.%20Nations%20are%20frantically%20scraping%20their%20coffers%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20citizens'%20basic%20needs%2C%20and%20we%20are%20standing%20farther%20from%20achieving%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-COVID%20international%20landscape%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20increasing%20geo-political%20and%20geo-economic%20tensions.%20In%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20the%20central%20theatre%20of%20global%20competition%2C%20several%20of%20these%20have%20culminated%20to%20present%20India%20with%20a%20series%20of%20challenging%20questions.%20These%20include%20navigating%20great%20power%20rivalry%2C%20conflicts%2C%20economic%20crises%2C%20deglobalisation%2C%20and%20adverse%20climate%20events%2C%20all%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20weakening%20multilateral%20order.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20each%20of%20these%20challenges%20is%20equally%20offset%20by%20opportunities%20for%20India.%20Most%20notably%20these%20include%20the%20chance%20to%20regain%20trust%20and%20leverage%20in%20its%20neighbourhood%2C%20gain%20from%20the%20relocation%20of%20global%20supply%20chains%2C%20expand%20cooperation%20with%20the%20west%2C%20push%20its%20agenda%20for%20clean%20energy%20transition%20and%20solidify%20its%20credentials%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20while%20steering%20international%20discourse%20and%20cooperation.%20Successful%20navigation%20of%20these%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20by%20India%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20elevate%20its%20status%20in%20the%20global%20order%20and%20ultimately%20provide%20it%20with%20crucial%20strategic%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20saw%20India%20taking%20on%20the%20global%20leadership%20role%20with%20aplomb%20as%20its%20G-20%20presidency%20gave%20New%20Delhi%20a%20chance%20to%20shape%20the%20agenda%20for%20global%20cooperation%20in%20a%20world%20emergingfrom%20the%20shadows%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20For%20India%2C%20this%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20underline%20its%20emerging%20status%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bleading%20power.%26quot%3B%20The%20G-20%20is%20unique%20in%20so%20far%20as%20it%20brings%20together%20the%20developed%20and%20the%20developing%20nations%20to%20discuss%20and%20create%20solutions%20to%20global%20governance%20challenges.%20New%20Delhi%20used%20this%20platform%20vociferous%20in%20giving%20voice%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20few%20global%20powers%20have%20neither%20the%20time%20nor%20resources%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20most%20vulnerable-occupied%20as%20they%20are%20with%20their%20own%20domestic%20woes.%20The%20pressures%20of%20global%20disruption%20are%20being%20absorbed%20most%20by%20the%20poorer%20economies%20and%20few%20powers%20are%20willing%20to%20consider%20their%20challenges%20with%20the%20seriousness%20they%20deserve.%20By%20hosting%20one%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20international%20gatherings%20ever%20at%20a%20time%20of%20great%20turbulence%20and%20managing%20to%20forge%20consensus%20among%20key%20global%20stakeholders%20despite%20fragmentation%2C%20New%20Delhi%20signalled%20its%20readiness%20to%20think%20big%20and%20deliver%20big-something%20that%20much%20of%20the%20world%20had%20long%20expected%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20India's%20desire%20to%20play%20a%20larger%20global%20role%20by%20not%20only%20participating%20in%20key%20global%20alliances%20and%20multilateral%20for%20a%20but%20also%20creating%20new%20ones%2C%20thereby%20demonstrating%20its%20commitment%20to%20collaborative%20and%20inclusive%20global%20governance%20in%20areas%20as%20diverse%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20sustainable%20development%2C%20global%20health%2C%20and%20peacekeeping.%20As%20a%20responsible%20global%20stakeholder%2C%20India's%20role%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20responder%26quot%3B%20during%20natural%20disasters%20or%20conflicts%20has%20been%20key%20in%20enhancing%20its%20global%20profile.%20From%20being%20a%20persistent%20naysayer%20to%20a%20nation%20willing%20to%20share%20responsibility%20for%20global%20governance%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20striking%20trends%20in%20Indian%20foreign%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20trend%20visible%20this%20year%20was%20India's%20continuing%20ability%20to%20balance%20its%20key%20partnerships.%20New%20Delhi's%20ties%20with%20major%20global%20powers%20continued%20to%20grow%20despite%20challenges.%20The%20Ukraine%20war%20did%20not%20create%20a%20rupture%20in%20India's%20ties%20with%20the%20West%2C%20something%20that%20was%20anticipated%20when%20the%20conflict%20had%20begun%20last%20year.%20Instead%2C%20these%20relations%20continued%20to%20grow%20and%20evolve.%20Despite%20the%20US%20accusations%20pertaining%20to%20the%20planned%20assassination%20of%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader%20and%20US%20citizen%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20Indo-US%20ties%20have%20retained%20their%20momentum%20with%20cooperation%20on%20critical%20and%20emerging%20technologies%20emerging%20as%20a%20key%20driver.%20The%20dramatic%20resurgence%20of%20the%20Quadrilateral%20Security%20Dialogue%20-%20the%20Quad%20-%20is%20the%20strongest%20manifestation%20of%20this%20new%20reality%20where%20the%20US%20and%20India%20are%20willing%20to%20forge%20a%20new%20partnership%20based%20on%20emerging%20realities.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20has%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20its%20close%20defence%20and%20strategic%20ties%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20aspect%20of%20India's%20external%20engagement%20this%20year%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20realisation%20that%20there%20is%20no%20substitute%20to%20building%20domestic%20capacities%20in%20critical%20sectors.%20Only%20a%20strong%20and%20self%20reliant%20India%20can%20take%20on%20an%20increasingly%20belligerent%20China%20and%20sustain%20it%20through%20regular%20systemic%20disruptions.%20If%20COVID-19%20alerted%20India%20to%20the%20need%20for%20self%20reliance%20in%20critical%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20made%20it%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20that%20lie%20ahead%20with%20an%20acute%20dependence%20on%20other%20actors%20for%20defence%20supplies.%20In%202023%2C%20India%20clocked%20its%20highest%20defence%20export%20value%20of%20Rs.15%2C920%20crores%20or%20roughly%20%245%20billion-10%20times%20more%20than%20the%20Rs.1%2C521%20crores%20it%20garnered%20in%202016-17%20for%20defence%20exports.%20This%20is%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20the%20country's%20burgeoning%20military-industrial%20complex%2C%20while%20also%20significant%20for%20the%20government's%20larger%20'Atmanirbhar'%20Initiative%2C%20where%20the%20defence%20industry%20is%20arguably%20leading%20the%20transition.%20In%20the%20economic%20realm%2C%20this%20has%20translated%20into%20a%20greater%20openness%20to%20forge%20substantive%20trade%20partnerships%20with%20like-minded%20nations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20inflection%20point%20for%20the%20global%20order%20and%20for%20India.%20India%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20achieving%20something%20dramatic%3A%20not%20only%20a%20top-tier%20economic%20power%20that%20is%20also%20a%20multicultural%20democracy%20but%20also%20a%20top-tier%20geopolitical%20player%20that%20can%20lead%2C%20not%20simply%20balance.%20The%20choices%20that%20New%20Delhi%20will%20make%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%20will%20define%20the%20contours%20of%20that%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Afghan%20Muddle%26quot%3B%20(HarperCollins)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703484480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Frog6itqs_delhi-generic_625x300_05_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-year-india-engaged-the-world-on-its-own-terms-4738184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20we%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20year%202023%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20global%20order%20that%20has%20been%20fundamentally%20reconfigured%20-%20politically%2C%20economically%20and%20diplomatically.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-year-india-engaged-the-world-on-its-own-terms-4738184%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-year-india-engaged-the-world-on-its-own-terms-4738184%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-year-india-engaged-the-world-on-its-own-terms-4738184%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hit%20Or%20Flop%3F%20Decoding%20The%20Curious%20Case%20Of%20Sanju%20Samson%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESanju%20Samson's%20talent%2C%20and%20potential%20if%20you%20could%20term%20it%20that%20at%20the%20age%20of%2029%2C%20is%20beyond%20reproach.%20An%20elegant%20stroke%20player%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20take%20any%20bowling%20attack%20in%20the%20world%20to%20the%20cleaners%2C%20Samson%20has%2C%20deservedly%2C%20earned%20a%20cult%20following%20for%20himself%2C%20mostly%20based%20on%20his%20performances%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%20Having%20made%20his%20IPL%20debut%20back%20in%202013%2C%20the%20wicket-keeper%20batsman%20has%20aged%20like%20fine%20wine%20in%20the%20domestic%20franchisee-based%20cricket%20league%2C%20getting%20better%20and%20better%20with%20every%20passing%20season.%20So%20far%2C%20Samson%20has%20amassed%203%2C888%20runs%20in%20152%20IPL%20outings%20with%20an%20average%20of%20close%20to%2030%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20137.19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20has%2C%20arguably%2C%20been%20the%20Kerala%20batter's%20best%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Having%20spent%20all%20but%20two%20seasons%20with%20Rajasthan%20Royals%2C%20Samson%20is%20RR's%20leading%20run%20scorer%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20was%20named%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20the%202021%20season.%20Under%20his%20stewardship%2C%20Rajasthan%20finished%20runners-up%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20whenever%20Sanju%20Samson%20has%20traded%20the%20Rajasthan%20colours%20for%20the%20blue%20stripes%20of%20the%20Indian%20national%20cricket%20team%2C%20he%20has%20been%20only%20a%20shadow%20of%20the%20maverick%20that%20he%20has%20been%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20his%20international%20debut%20in%20a%20T20I%20against%20Zimbabwe%20back%20in%202015%2C%20it%20took%20Samson%20eight%20long%20years%20to%20log%20his%20first%20international%20century%20-%20108%20vs%20South%20Africa%20in%20an%20ODI%20at%20Paarl%20on%20December%2021%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20fairness%2C%20it%20was%20not%20till%202020%20that%20Samson%20made%20his%20second%20international%20appearance%20in%20a%20T20I%20vs%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Pune.%20He%20only%20made%20his%20ODI%20debut%20in%202021%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20earn%20his%20maiden%20Test%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20loyal%20Sanju%20Samson%20fans%20may%20argue%20that%20the%20batter%20hasn't%20had%20enough%20opportunities%20to%20prove%20himself%20on%20the%20international%20stage%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20classy%20right-handed%20batter%20has%20hardly%20done%20justice%20to%20his%20talents%20when%20the%20chances%20did%20come%20his%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20T20Is%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%20has%20scored%20only%20374%20runs%20in%2024%20outings%20at%20an%20average%20just%20short%20of%2020%20-%20no%20doubt%20a%20disappointing%20record%20considering%20his%20heroics%20in%20the%20same%20format%20of%20cricket%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20what's%20the%20most%20worrisome%20part%20about%20Samson's%20knocks%20is%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20get%20good%20starts.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20converting%20these%20into%20big%20knocks%2C%20the%20Kerala%20batter%20has%20come%20off%20short%2C%20especially%20against%20good%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamson's%20highest%20score%20in%20T20I%20cricket%20is%2077%20vs%20Ireland%20-%20his%20only%20half-century%20in%20the%20format.%20His%20second-highest%20score%20is%2040%2C%20which%20came%20against%20the%20same%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamson's%20ODI%20record%2C%20however%2C%20paints%20a%20different%20picture.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20despite%20making%20only%2016%20appearances%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%2C%20he%20has%20amassed%20510%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2056.66.%20Staying%20unbeaten%20in%20five%20of%20the%2014%20innings%20he%20has%20batted%20in%20contributes%20heavily%20to%20the%20high%20average%20but%20irrespective%20of%20the%20fact%2C%20someone%20with%20an%20average%20of%2050%20plus%20is%20hard%20to%20ignore%20while%20picking%20any%20ODI%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20a%20different%20challenge%20Samson%20faces%20here.%20As%20a%20wicketkeeper-batsman%2C%20Samson%2C%20now%2029%2C%20will%20be%20pitted%20against%20the%20likes%20of%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%2026%2C%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%2025.%20Both%20players%20already%20have%20a%20proven%20pedigree%20in%20international%20cricket%20and%20their%20age%20makes%20them%20better%20long-term%20prospects%20for%20selectors%2C%20who%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20prepare%20a%20team%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20considered%20in%20the%20team%20a%20specialist%20batter%2C%20Sanju%20Samson's%20preferred%20position%20is%20the%20No.%203%20slot%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20always%20reserved%20for%20one%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20when%20fit%20and%20not%20rested.%20Samson's%20aggressive%20style%20of%20play%20also%20allows%20him%20to%20play%20as%20a%20finisher%20but%20on%20that%20front%2C%20again%2C%20Samson%20has%20competition%20with%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20and%20the%20fast-emerging%20Rinku%20Singh%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant's%20inevitable%20return%20post%20his%20unfortunate%20accident%20back%20in%202022%2C%20will%20only%20make%20the%20competition%20tougher%20for%20Samson%20to%20cement%20his%20place%20in%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabelling%20Sanju%20Samson's%20international%20career%20a%20hit%20or%20flop%20isn't%20quite%20a%20straightforward%20call.%20But%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20it's%20been%20a%20story%20of%20missed%20opportunities%20-%20several%20of%20them%20-%20and%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20competition%20to%20get%20into%20the%20Indian%20men's%20cricket%20team%20has%20been%20the%20fiercest%20it%20has%20ever%20been%2C%20it's%20a%20luxury%20no%20player%2C%20even%20someone%20of%20Sanju%20Samson's%20calibre%2C%20can%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703484480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhskphjh_sanju-samson-afp_625x300_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhit-or-flop-decoding-the-curious-case-of-sanju-samson-4728415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impressive%20Indian%20batters%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20Sanju%20Samson's%20international%20career%20has%20been%20a%20tale%20of%20missed%20opportunities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhit-or-flop-decoding-the-curious-case-of-sanju-samson-4728415%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhit-or-flop-decoding-the-curious-case-of-sanju-samson-4728415%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhit-or-flop-decoding-the-curious-case-of-sanju-samson-4728415%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%2037%2C000%20Women%20Perform%20%26quot%3BMaha%20Raas%26quot%3B%20In%20Gujarat's%20Dwarka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%2037%2C000%20women%2C%20wearing%20vibrant%20red%20attire%2C%20congregated%20in%20Gujarat's%20Dwarka%20for%20the%20Maha%20Raas%2C%20a%20two-day%20event%20held%20on%20December%2023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%2C%20dedicated%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20Raas%20by%20Usha%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Banasur%20and%20daughter-in-law%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20captivated%20attendees%20with%20synchronised%20dances%20around%20an%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Krishna.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrone%20footage%20shows%20thousands%20of%20women%20belonging%20to%20the%20Ahir%20community%20circling%20the%20Lord%20Krishna%20idol%20while%20spectators%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Ahirani%20Maharash%