uman-rights-message%252Fnews-story%252Fa79c9c1516461fd601daa175a2fa1106%26memtype%3Danonymous%26mode%3Dpremium%26v21%3DGROUPA-Segment-1-NOSCORE%26V21spcbehaviour%3Dappend%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Weekend%20Australian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20had%20been%20most%20other%20organisations%20that%20showed%20some%20semblance%20of%20consistency%20with%20their%20attitude%20and%20behaviour%20on%20issues%20I%20could%20claim%20surprise%2C%20but%20not%20them.%20Once%20again%2C%20they%20show%20their%20hypocrisy%20and%20lack%20of%20moral%20standing%20as%20an%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20his%20mind%2C%20Holding%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20movement%20that%20got%20support%20from%20ICC%20as%20well%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20regulations%20say%20re%20messaging%20'approval%20shall%20not%20be%20granted%20for%20messages%20which%20relate%20to%20political%2C%20religious%20or%20racial%20activities%20or%20causes'.%20So%20how%20the%20f***%20people%20were%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20knee%20for%20BLM%20and%20stumps%20were%20covered%20with%20LGBTQ%20colours%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20latest%2C%20Khawaja%20has%20reportedly%20been%20denied%20permission%20to%20place%20a%20peace%20symbol%20on%20his%20bat%20and%20shoes%20for%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20against%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sticker%20showing%20a%20black%20dove%20and%20the%20words%2001%3AUDHR%20--%20a%20reference%20to%20Article%20One%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20--%20was%20on%20his%20bat%20and%20shoes%20during%20training%20in%20Melbourne%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20star%20batter%20had%20multiple%20meetings%20with%20Cricket%20Australia%20over%20recent%20days%20to%20find%20a%20message%20that%20would%20be%20appropriate%20for%20the%20second%20Test%20this%20week%2C%20local%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%