on't%20even%20have%20houses%20to%20go%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ala'a%20Salameh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20owners%20of%20Afteem%20Restaurant%2C%20a%20family-owned%20falafel%20restaurant%20just%20steps%20from%20the%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalameh%20said%20Christmas%20Eve%20is%20usually%20the%20busiest%20day%20of%20the%20year.%20%26quot%3BNormally%2C%20you%20can't%20find%20a%20single%20chair%20to%20sit%2C%20we're%20full%20from%20morning%20till%20midnight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Salameh.%20On%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20just%20one%20table%20was%20taken%2C%20by%20journalists%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20the%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20banner%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BBethlehem's%20Christmas%20bells%20ring%20for%20a%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20few%20teenagers%20offered%20small%20inflatable%20Santas%2C%20but%20no%20one%20was%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20their%20traditional%20march%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20Bethlehem%2C%20young%20scouts%20stood%20silently%20with%20flags.%20A%20group%20of%20local%20students%20unfurled%20a%20massive%20Palestinian%20flag%20as%20they%20stood%20in%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20organist%20with%20the%20Church%20of%20the%20Nativity%20choir%2C%20Shukry%20Mubarak%2C%20said%20the%20group%20changed%20much%20of%20the%20traditional%20Christmas%20musical%20repertoire%20from%20joyful%20holiday%20songs%20to%20more%20solemn%20hymns%20in%20minor%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20message%20every%20year%20on%20Christmas%20is%20one%20of%20peace%20and%20love%2C%20but%20this%20year%20it's%20a%20message%20of%20sadness%2C%20grief%20and%20anger%20in%20front%20of%20the%20international%20community%20with%20what%20is%20happening%20and%20going%20on%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20Bethlehem's%20mayor%2C%20Hana%20Haniyeh%2C%20said%20in%20an%20address%20to%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Joseph%20Mugasa%2C%20a%20pediatrician%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20international%20visitors.%20He%20said%20his%20tour%20group