tmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatin%20Patriarch%20Pierbattista%20Pizzaballa%2C%20arriving%20from%20Jerusalem%20for%20the%20traditional%20procession%20to%20the%20Church%20of%20the%20Nativity%2C%20told%20the%20sparse%20crowd%20that%20Christmas%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Breason%20to%20hope%26quot%3B%20despite%20the%20war%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pared-down%20Christmas%20was%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20original%20message%20of%20the%20holiday%20and%20illustrated%20the%20many%20ways%20the%20community%20is%20coming%20together%2C%20said%20Stephanie%20Salda%C3%B1a%2C%20who%20is%20originally%20from%20San%20Antonio%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20Jerusalem%20and%20Bethlehem%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20a%20parish%20priest%20at%20the%20St%20Joseph%20Syriac%20Catholic%20Church.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20Christmas%20as%20more%20real%20than%20ever%2C%20because%20we're%20waiting%20for%20the%20prince%20of%20peace%20to%20come.%20We%20are%20waiting%20for%20a%20miracle%20to%20stop%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Salda%C3%B1a%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbethlehem-is-a-ghost-town-due-to-israel-hamas-war-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703461574000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6588c2421c5c7b8c9a0bda2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbethlehem-is-a-ghost-town-due-to-israel-hamas-war-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bethlehem's%20economy%20depends%20on%20Christmas%20tourists.%20But%20officials%20in%20Jesus'%20traditional%20birthplace%20are%20forgoing%20celebrations%20due%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A522%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbethlehem-is-a-ghost-town-due-to-israel-hamas-war-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAm