eople%20can%20buy%20all%20your%20crawfish%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20season%20and%20then%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20catch%20picks%20up%20they%20can%20leave%20you%20and%20buy%20from%20somebody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smaller%20crawfish%2C%20McIntyre%20sells%20to%20himself%20to%20use%20in%20his%20restaurants%20and%20other%20products.%20These%20crawfish%20are%20sent%20to%20a%20separate%20factory%20to%20have%20their%20tail%20meat%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crawfish%20are%20first%20dumped%20into%20tanks%20before%20they%20are%20washed%20a%20second%20time%2C%20then%20they%20are%20dropped%20into%20a%20large%20basket%20that%20is%20dropped%20into%20a%20huge%20pot%20of%20boiling%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221836%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Parish%20Seafood%20Wholesale%20worker%20lowering%20a%20basket%20of%20crawfish%20into%20a%20vat%20of%20boiling%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65887f181c5c7b8c9a0bd969%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22922%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Parish%20Seafood%20Wholesale%20worker%20lowering%20a%20basket%20of%20crawfish%20into%20a%20vat%20of%20boiling%20water.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20boiling%2C%20the%20crawfish%20are%20taken%20to%20a%20peeling%20room%2C%20where%20they%20are%20peeled%20by%20hand.%20Leona%20Williams%2C%20a%20peeler%20in%20the%20facility%2C%20says%20she%20has%20been%20peeling%20there%20for%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLearned%20this%20from%20momma%20at%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BGet%20off%20of%20school%2C%20help%20my%20mom%20sometimes%20until%20one%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%2C%20who%20can%20peel%20about%2040%20pounds%20of%20crawfish%20daily%2C%20says%20you%20have%20to%20break%20the%20head%20off%20the%20crawfish%20first%20before%20pinching%20the%20tail%20to%20pull%20out%20its%20meat.%3C%2Fp%