%2Fsanta-banned-army-aircraft%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETask%20%26amp%3B%20Purpose%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20reported.%20The%20policy%20notes%20that%20any%20such%20trip%20must%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20that%20travelers%20must%20wear%20%26quot%3Bproper%20organizational%20uniforms%2C%20if%20applicable%2C%20and%20must%20present%20proper%20identification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20officials%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Santa%20has%20been%20on%20the%20service's%20%26quot%3BNo-Fly%20List%26quot%3B%20for%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20century.%20They%20said%20the%20regulation's%20%26quot%3Boriginal%20intent%20is%20lost%20to%20the%20ghosts%20of%20Christmas%20Past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20research%2C%20some%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20regulation%20was%20put%20in%20place%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20propriety%20or%20possibly%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryce%20Dubee%2C%20an%20Army%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20over%20the%20years%20on%20special%20occasions%2C%20hardworking%20Army%20elves%20have%20been%20granted%20exceptions%20to%20the%20policy%20to%20allow%20Kris%20Kringle%20to%20join%20them%20in%20support%20of%20holiday%20missions%2C%20such%20as%20Operation%20Toy%20Drop%20and%20Operation%20Santa%20Claus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOperation%20Toy%20Drop%20is%20an%20annual%20event%20during%20which%20soldiers%20parachute%20to%20the%20ground%20for%20a%20crowd%20of%20spectators.%20Toy%20donations%20are%20also%20collected%2C%20which%20the%20Army%20distributes%20to%20local%20partners%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-army%2F2018%2F11%2F28%2Fcome-on-down-to-fort-bragg-this-week-for-operation-toy-drop%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArmy%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20event%20is%20an%20exercise%20to%20train%20allied%20jumpmasters%20to%20work%20with%20US%20active%20duty%20and%20Air%20Force%20Reserve%20Command%20paratroopers%2C%20accord