20in%20for%20questioning%3F%20They%20made%20it%20seem%20so%20normal%2C%20they%20phoned%20him%20up%20to%20come%20to%20the%20camp%E2%80%9D%20lamented%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20just%20worked%20with%20them%20but%20also%20stood%20by%20them%20on%20this%20uncertain%20border%2C%20this%20is%20our%20reward%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Army%20has%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20matter%20is%20under%20investigation%20and%20that%20it%20stands%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadgpi%2Fstatus%2F1738548583769759899%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommitted%20to%20extending%20full%20support%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20cooperation%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20investigations%E2%80%9D%2C%20locals%20believe%20the%20bond%20between%20them%20and%20the%20Army%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20rebuild.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20has%20not%20specified%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20deaths%2C%20but%20has%20said%20legal%20action%20had%20been%20initiated%20and%20compensation%20announced.%20On%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJKCDC_%2Fstatus%2F1738762558688075973%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20was%20reported%20yesterday%20in%20Baffliaz%20of%20Poonch%20District.%20The%20medico%20legal%20formalities%20were%20conducted%20and%20legal%20action%20in%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%20Government%20has%20announced%20compensation%20for%20each%20of%20the%20deceased.%20Further%20Government%20also%20announced%20compassionate%20appointments%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20each%20deceased.%E