s%20a%20film%20less%20about%20any%20frenetic%20onscreen%20shenanigans%20as%20it%20is%20about%20its%20own%20mood%20board%20of%20sartorial%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guy%20Lodge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-crime-is-mine-review-1235850129%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20the%20IMA%20Cheering%20If%20Doctors%20Are%20Still%20Punishable%20for%20Medical%20Negligence%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F01124355%2FDYF-camp.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%2022%20December%2C%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20organisation%20representing%20doctors%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20extended%20its%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20via%20a%20daily%20newspaper%20advertisement%20for%20%E2%80%9Cexempting%20medical%20professionals%20from%20criminal%20prosecution%20under%20304(a)%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20now%2026%20of%20BNS%20(death%20by%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gesture%20followed%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20in%20Parliament%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20the%20three%20criminal%20reform%20Bills%20were%20passed%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20provisions%20related%20to%20death%20resulting%20from%20medical%20negligence%20would%20be%20excluded%20from%20Section%2026%20of%20the%20new%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pledged%20an%20amendment%20to%20shield%20doctors%20from%20potential%20legal%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20not%20exempt%20from%20punishment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20passage%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20doctors%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20receive%20outright%20immunity%20in%20cases%20of%20death%20due%20to%20negligence%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20BNS.%20Instead%2C%20the%20legislation%20maintains%20a%20maximum%20two-year%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20this%20is%20a%20slightly%20reduced%20penalty%20compared%20to%20other%20death-related%20offences%2C%20the%20punishments%20for%20which%20have%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20BNS%2C%20the%20punishment%20for%20causing%20accidental%20death%20(like%20road%20traffic%20death)%20was%20increased%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20five%20years.%20An%20additional%20provision%20was%20introduced%20for%20situations%20where%20the%20responsible%20party%20flees%20or%20fails%20to%20report%20the%20incident%2C%20allowing%20for%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20amendment%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20such%20an%20act%20is%20done%20by%20a%20registered%20medical%20practitioner%20while%20performing%20a%20medical%20procedure%2C%20he%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20two%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20a%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20criminal%20cases%20can%20still%20be%20filed%20against%20medical%20professionals%20for%20deaths%20arising%20from%20medical%20negligence%2C%20but%20the%20maximum%20imprisonment%20is%20now%20less%20severe%20compared%20to%20other%20death-related%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20why%20is%20the%20IMA%20happy%20about%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20will%20maintain%20the%20maximum%20imprisonment%20for%20doctors%20at%20the%20same%20level%20as%20specified%20under%20Section%20304(A)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20allowing%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20original%20draft%20of%20the%20Bill%20had%20asked%20for%20seven%20years%20of%20punishment%20for%20death%20due%20to%20negligence.%20We%20made%20a%20submission%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20to%20differentiate%20medical%20death%20by%20a%20doctor%20from%20death%20due%20to%20negligence.%20Later%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20lowered%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20President-elect%20of%20IMA%2C%20Dr%20V%20Asokan%2C%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Home%20Minister%20accepted%20the%20demand%20and%20differentiated%20medical%20negligence.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20the%20minister%20went%20beyond%20this%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20explicitly%20stating%20that%20deaths%20during%20treatment%20were%20no%20longer%20to%20be%20considered%20as%20murder.%20The%20minister%20expressed%20the%20intention%20to%20exempt%20doctors%20from%20such%20scenarios%20through%20an%20upcoming%20amendment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Asokan%20added%20that%20the%20parliamentary%20declaration%20by%20the%20Home%20Minister%20signifies%20a%20departure%20from%20previous%20norms%2C%20affirming%20that%20any%20death%20during%20treatment%20is%20not%20to%20be%20deemed%20as%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20essence%2C%20the%20government%20has%20declared%2C%20in%20principle%2C%20its%20acceptance%20of%20the%20IMA%E2%80%99s%20stance%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminality%20involved%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient.%20The%20IMA%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminal%20intention%20between%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient%2C%20emphasising%20that%20criminality%20requires%20intent%20to%20harm%2C%20and%20crime%20is%20defined%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20criminal%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20negligence%20as%20per%20the%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20negligence%20is%20subject%20to%20provisions%20influenced%20by%20case%20laws%2C%20particularly%20relevant%20Supreme%20Court%20judgements%20like%20Jacob%20Mathew%20vs%20State%20of%20Punjab%2C%20dealing%20with%20medical%20negligence%20and%20the%20criminal%20liability%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20and%20resulted%20in%20the%20formulation%20of%20important%20guidelines%20regarding%20the%20prosecution%20of%20doctors%20for%20offences%20related%20to%20medical%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20a%20doctor%2C%20Jacob%20Mathew%2C%20accused%20of%20causing%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20death%20due%20to%20medical%20negligence.%20Dr%20Mathew%20challenged%20criminal%20proceedings%2C%20arguing%20that%20a%20medical%20professional%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20held%20criminally%20liable%20for%20an%20error%20of%20judgement%20or%20a%20bona%20fide%20mistake%20while%20treating%20a%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%202005%20judgment%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20doctors%20from%20frivolous%20criminal%20prosecutions%20but%20emphasised%20accountability%20in%20cases%20of%20genuine%20medical%20negligence.%20The%20court%20laid%20down%20guidelines%20to%20differentiate%20between%20genuine%20errors%20and%20acts%20of%20negligence%20by%20medical%20practitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20points%20from%20the%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Gross%20Negligence%20Standard%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20held%20that%20for%20a%20doctor%20to%20be%20held%20criminally%20liable%2C%20the%20negligence%20should%20be%20of%20such%20a%20high%20degree%20as%20to%20amount%20to%20gross%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Intentional%20Acts%20or%20Omissions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20clarified%20that%20criminal%20liability%20would%20arise%20only%20if%20a%20medical%20professional%E2%80%99s%20act%20or%20omission%20is%20so%20reckless%20or%20negligent%20that%20it%20can%20be%20equated%20with%20a%20criminal%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Professional%20Standards%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20high%20professional%20standards%20and%20medical%20ethics%2C%20and%20that%20a%20breach%20of%20these%20standards%20could%20be%20a%20ground%20for%20criminal%20liability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Expert%20Opinion%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20court%20highlighted%20the%20significance%20of%20obtaining%20expert%20opinion%20to%20establish%20negligence%2C%20and%20that%20the%20opinion%20should%20be%20given%20by%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20same%20field%20as%20the%20one%20being%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jacob%20Mathew%20case%20has%20since%20been%20cited%20in%20various%20judgements%20related%20to%20medical%20negligence%20in%20India%20and%20provided%20a%20framework%20for%20determining%20when%20criminal%20liability%20may%20be%20imposed%20on%20medical%20practitioners%20for%20their%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20it%20mean%20for%20patients%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Asokan%20added%20that%20there%20is%20always%20the%20possibility%20of%20seeking%20civil%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20negligence%2C%20which%20aligns%20with%20what%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Claw%20of%20thoughts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20medical%20profession%20falls%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20this%20law%20and%20while%20we%20adhere%20to%20it%2C%20our%20contention%20lies%20in%20distinguishing%20it%20from%20criminal%20negligence.%20In%20the%20realm%20of%20criminal%20law%2C%20intent%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%2C%20often%20denoted%20by%20the%20Latin%20term%20%E2%80%98mens%20rea%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20exists%20a%20distinction%20between%20a%20doctor-patient%20relationship%20and%20instances%20of%20medical%20negligence%20or%20accidents%2C%20such%20as%20unpredictable%20events%2C%20like%20anaesthetic%20deaths%2C%20which%20are%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20medical%20accidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20IMA%E2%80%99s%20stance%20emphasised%20that%20the%20medical%20profession%20complies%20with%20the%20law%20of%20civil%20compensation%20and%20the%20law%20of%20thoughts%2C%20but%20it%20rejects%20the%20notion%20of%20criminal%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20position%20has%20found%20support%20from%20the%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20On%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20expressed%20intention%20to%20amend%20the%20law%2C%20stating%20that%20in%20the%20context%20of%20treatment%2C%20there%20is%20no%20murder%20involved%2C%20and%20doctors%20can%20be%20exempted.%20This%20statement%20marks%20a%20departure%20from%20what%20the%20government%20had%20previously%20articulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Asokan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20civil%20liabilities%2C%20the%20consumer%20commission%20is%20the%20available%20platform%20for%20patients%20who%20find%20doctors%20and%20hospitals%20liable%20for%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20hospitals%20and%20doctors%20are%20covered%20under%20indemnity%20insurance%2C%20a%20financial%20arrangement%20that%20provides%20protection%20against%20potential%20losses%20or%20damages%20by%20compensating%20doctors%20for%20covered%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Asokan%2C%20the%20new%20law%20is%20advantageous%20for%20both%20doctors%20and%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20event%20of%20a%20loss%2C%20patients%E2%80%99%20families%20can%20pursue%20civil%20suits%20without%20doctors%20being%20perceived%20as%20criminals%20or%20murderers.%20This%20instils%20confidence%20in%20doctors%2C%20especially%20in%20critical%20situations%2C%20eliminating%20the%20fear%20of%20imprisonment%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20calculated%20risks.%20The%20beneficiaries%20here%20are%20both%20the%20patient%20and%20the%20doctor%2C%20making%20it%20a%20positive%20development%20for%20public%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Asokan%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2F%5C%22%3E%20South%20First%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Read%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fhealth%2Fima-hails-legal-safeguard-doctors-gratitude-as-new-legislation-curbs-criminal-prosecution-in-cases-of-medical-negligence%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703420441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F01124355%2FDYF-camp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-is-the-ima-cheering-if-doctors-are-still-punishable-for-medical-negligence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IMA%20is%20happy%20that%20the%20new%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20differentiates%20medical%20negligence%20from%20criminal%20offence%2C%20and%20offers%20a%20less%20harsh%20punishment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-is-the-ima-cheering-if-doctors-are-still-punishable-for-medical-negligence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spotting%20a%20Real%20Democracy%20Amid%20the%20Fakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20the%20ongoing%20cacophony%20of%20news%20and%20deep%20fake%20news%2C%20claims%20and%20counter%20claims%2C%20dissemination%20and%20dissembling%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%20between%20fake%20and%20genuine%20democracies.%20What%20makes%20a%20country%20a%20real%20democracy%3F%20Is%20it%20a%20progressive%20and%20liberal%20constitution%3F%20An%20independent%20judiciary%3F%20A%20fearless%20press%20and%20media%3F%20An%20elected%20government%3F%20An%20independent%20civil%20service%3F%20On%20paper%2C%20yes.%20But%20in%20reality%20these%20attributes%20are%20neither%20sufficient%20nor%20enough%20to%20ensure%20a%20democratic%20government%20or%20a%20free%20society.%20This%20is%20being%20demonstrated%20to%20us%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20right%20here%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20sake%20of%20appearances%2C%20and%20press%20releases%2C%20India%20has%20all%20the%20attributes%20mentioned%20above%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20a%20different%20kettle%20of%20fish%20altogether.%20There%20is%20little%20point%20in%20listing%20out%20what%20has%20gone%20wrong%20with%20our%20constitution%2C%20judiciary%2C%20press%20and%20the%20civil%20services%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20for%20they%20are%20all%20well%20documented%20and%20known%20to%20those%20who%20care%20about%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20(retired)%20Rohinton%20Fali%20Nariman%20listed%20out%20the%20four%20developments%20this%20year%20which%20have%20disturbed%20him%20most.%20The%20top%20court%20has%20yet%20to%20give%20any%20judgment%20of%20any%20consequence%20where%20it%20has%20spoken%20against%20the%20Union%20government%3B%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20become%20some%20kind%20of%20philosopher%E2%80%99s%20stone%20which%20can%20turn%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20dross%20into%20the%20gold%20of%20victories%3B%20the%20parliament%20has%20become%20a%20vestigial%20appendage%20like%20the%20coccyx%20in%20the%20human%20body%20which%20has%20long%20outlived%20its%20utility%20and%20has%20to%20be%20cast%20aside%3B%20and%20the%20civil%20services%20(and%20the%20defence%20forces)%20have%20either%20become%20camp%20followers%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%20or%20have%20hunkered%20down%20in%20their%20well%20cushioned%20burrows%20like%20the%20marmots%20in%20the%20More%20plains%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-trying-to-change-caste-apartheid-system-in-india-not-a-free-democracy-anymore%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3A%20%E2%80%98Trying%20to%20Change%20Caste%20%E2%80%98Apartheid%E2%80%99%20System%20in%20India%2C%20Not%20a%20Free%20Democracy%20Anymore%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20have%20become%20what%20political%20scientist%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%20has%20termed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo%20constitutional%20facade%E2%80%9D%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20For%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20we%20are%20an%20eroding%20democracy%20and%20an%20uncaring%20society%2C%20and%20this%20can%20be%20best%20understood%20by%20a%20comparison%20with%20some%20other%2C%20more%20genuine%2C%20democracies.%20Comparisons%20are%20odious%2C%20but%20they%20are%20sometimes%20necessary%20to%20recognise%20our%20hidden%20ugliness.%20Just%20a%20couple%20of%20examples%20should%20suffice%20to%20make%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20our%20government%E2%80%99s%20and%20society%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict.%20Any%20criticism%20of%20Israel%20is%20not%20allowed%3A%20lectures%20are%20not%20permitted%2C%20protests%20are%20banned%2C%20police%20cases%20are%20filed%20against%20those%20who%20dare%20to%20put%20up%20posts%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20media%20will%20not%20show%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20story%2C%20celebrities%20and%20influencers%20are%20conspicuously%20silent%2C%20all%20in%20thrall%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20the%20settler-colonial%20policy%20of%20Israel%20and%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20same%20developed%20world%2C%20and%20indeed%20within%20Israel%20itself%2C%20there%20are%20no%20restrictions%20on%20the%20expression%20of%20the%20wide-spread%20anger%20against%20Israel.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20being%20condemned%20by%20the%20US%20media%20daily%20for%20supporting%20the%20slaughter%20in%20Gaza.%20Even%20his%20state%20department%20officials%20are%20staging%20a%20kind%20of%20mini%20revolt%2C%20expressing%20their%20dissent%20through%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdissent%20line%E2%80%9D%20created%20for%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-300x158.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26225238%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-10.51.1-1024x538.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681946%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Jewish%20protester%20in%20a%20pro-Palestine%20demonstration%20in%20the%20US.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40jvplive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20opinion%20is%20turning%20against%20him.%20In%20November%2C%20journalists%20with%20the%20BBC%20protested%20against%20their%20own%20management%20for%20being%20selective%20in%20its%20coverage%20of%20the%20war%2C%20dehumanising%20Palestinians%20and%20failing%20to%20show%20the%20Israeli%20atrocities.%20Universities%20are%20pushing%20back%20against%20their%20pro-Israel%20funders%20who%20want%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20anti-Jewish%20sentiments%20on%20the%20campuses%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20president%20has%20resigned.%20Public%20protests%20are%20being%20staged%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Australia%20and%20Canada%20with%20people%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza.%20None%20of%20these%20governments%20can%20even%20consider%20suppressing%20these%20protests%2C%20and%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20these%20will%20have%20their%20effect%20on%20the%20policies%20of%20these%20countries.%20This%20is%20how%20genuine%20democracies%20give%20voice%20to%20their%20citizens%E2%80%99%20concerns%20against%20their%20own%20governments%20turning%20rogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London%20Metropolitan%20police%20recently%20provided%20another%20example%20of%20how%20real%20democracies%20work.%20Various%20organisations%20had%20planned%20a%20massive%20march%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine%20on%20Armistice%20Day%20last%20month.%20British%20Home%20Secretary%20Suella%20Braverman%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Uncle%20Tom%20(brazenly%20pro-Israel)%20wanted%20the%20police%20to%20deny%20permission%20for%20it.%20The%20police%20commissioner%20refused%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20there%20was%20no%20threat%20to%20law%20and%20order%20and%20he%20could%20not%20legally%20ban%20the%20march.%20Braverman%20went%20public%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20accusing%20the%20London%20police%20of%20partisanship%20and%20selective%20favouritism.%20The%20commissioner%20stood%20his%20ground%2C%20the%20march%20went%20ahead%20peacefully%2C%20the%20only%20arrests%20were%20of%20some%20right%20wing%20elements%20who%20attempted%20to%20disrupt%20it.%20And%20guess%20what%3F%20There%20was%20so%20much%20anger%20and%20outrage%20against%20Braverman%20that%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20to%20sack%20the%20her.%20This%20is%20how%20democracies%20work.%20Not%20like%20our%20own%20police%20who%20have%20become%20like%20private%20militias%20of%20any%20ruling%20party%2C%20whether%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Union%20or%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-last-pillar-of-indian-democracy-has-fallen%5C%22%3EThe%20Last%20Pillar%20of%20Indian%20Democracy%20Has%20Fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20defence%20chiefs%20are%20looking%20increasingly%20like%20men%20of%20straw%2C%20not%20withstanding%20their%20impressively%20resplendent%20uniforms%2C%20with%20more%20stars%20than%20in%20the%20Milky%20Way.%20They%20have%20been%20silent%20even%20as%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20run%20rough%20shod%20over%20their%20decades%20old%20culture%20and%20ethos%2C%20changing%20their%20regimental%20traditions%2C%20ranks%2C%20uniforms%2C%20mode%20of%20recruitment%2C%20perhaps%20even%20interfering%20in%20operational%20and%20tactical%20matters.%20And%20now%2C%20we%20are%20told%2C%20some%20of%20these%20retired%20worthies%20may%20even%20be%20attending%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20a%20politico-religious%20event%2C%20further%20eroding%20the%20apolitical%20and%20religion-neutral%20ethos%20of%20our%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompare%20this%20with%20the%20stance%20adopted%20by%20General%20Milley%2C%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20US%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%2C%20who%20resisted%20every%20move%20by%20Trump%20to%20use%20the%20military%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20power.%20He%20made%20his%20reservations%20clear%20to%20the%20White%20House%20and%20almost%20resigned%20in%20June%202020%2C%20but%20then%20told%20his%20staff%3A%20%E2%80%9D%20If%20they%20want%20to%20court-martial%20me%20or%20put%20me%20in%20prison%2C%20have%20at%20it%E2%80%A6.I%20will%20fight%20from%20the%20inside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20democracies%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20fake%20ones.%20respect%20their%20citizens%E2%80%99%20sentiments%2C%20do%20not%20suppress%20them%20by%20the%20use%20of%20force%2C%20and%20have%20robust%20institutions%20and%20civil%20societies%20that%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted%20at%20critical%20moments.%20We%20are%20not%20yet%20a%20fake%20democracy%2C%20but%20we%20are%20getting%20there%20fast.%20Democracies%20do%20not%20die%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20governments%20alone%3A%20when%20public%20conscience%20and%20opinion%20dies%2C%20so%20do%20democracies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favayshukla.blogspot.com%2F2023%2F12%2Ffake-democracies-and-real-ones.html%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20blog%2C%20View%20from%20%5BGreater%5D%20Kailash.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703420190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fspotting-a-real-democracy-amid-the-fakes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Democracies%20do%20not%20die%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20governments%20alone.%20When%20public%20conscience%20and%20opinion%20dies%2C%20so%20do%20democracies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fspotting-a-real-democracy-amid-the-fakes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thieves%20steal%20seafood%20and%20meat%20worth%20thousands%20days%20before%20Christmas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-cctv-australia-meat_6403205.jpg%3F20231224112711%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthieves-steal-seafood-and-meat-worth-thousands-from-australian-butcher-days-before-christmas-13037315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20thieves%20have%20raided%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20worth%20of%20seafood%20and%20meat%20from%20a%20butchers%20in%20South%20Australia%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%2