need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20saying%20that%20it%20reveals%20the%20composition%20of%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20which%20will%20will%20open%20up%20a%20window%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government%20was%20attempting%20to%20turn%20India%20into%20a%20nation%20with%20%E2%80%9Cone%20ideology%2C%20one%20religion%20and%20one%20language.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20they%20kill%20the%20negotiation%2C%20they%20try%20to%20capture%20the%20institutions.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20really%20the%20political%20fight%20in%20India%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20if%20you%20end%20the%20negotiation%20in%20India%2C%20the%20conversation%20between%20the%20union%20India%20collapses%2C%20India%20tears%20itself%20apart.So%20you%20can%20see%20that%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20you%20can%20see%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20burning.%20You%20can%20see%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20a%20problem.%20As%20somebody%20said%20to%20me%20the%20other%20day%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20edges.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20a%20system%20you%20got%20to%20look%20at%20the%20edges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20scale%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D%20is%20underway%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20economic%20inequality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassively%20concentrating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20economic%20development%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20in%20whose%20interest%20is%20that%20economic%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20next%20to%20the%20figure%20of%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20the%20figure%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20So%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%2C%20but%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20growing%20is%20by%20massively%20concentrating%20wealth%20towards%20very%20few%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEconomic%20growth%20without%20meaningful%20employment%20fosters%20inequality%20and%20undermines%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20only%20a%20few%20close%20wealthy%20friends%20of%20the%20government%20are%20benefiting%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20growth%2C%20leaving%20common%20Indians%20grappling%20with%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEyHC1SpmwI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEyHC1SpmwI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1738833537082802422%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilar%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20are%20operating%20on%20a%20debt%20sort%20of%20model%20and%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20producing.%20The%20real%20challenge%20in%20India%20is%20how%20do%20we%20set%20up%20a%20production%20economy%20that%20is%20able%20to%20give%20large%20numbers%20of%20people%20jobs.%20We%20have%20two%20or%20three%20businesses%20that%20are%20pretty%20much%20entire%20business%20system.%20We%20have%20Mr%20%5BGautam%5D%20Adani%2C%20everybody%20knows%20he%20is%20dir