20regular%20feature%2C%20alongside%20six%20siblings.%20Hip%20Hop%20came%20into%20Moko%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20he%20was%20barely%20nine%20after%20listening%20to%20iconic%20rapper%20Eminem%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%988%20Mile%E2%80%99%20CD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20others%20like%2050%20Cent%20and%20Ja-Rule%20who%20were%20beefing%20at%20the%20time%20and%20putting%20out%20music%2C%20but%20the%20first%20Hip%20Hop%20artist%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20was%20Eminem.%20His%20fearless%20storytelling%2C%20humour%20and%20the%20music%20itself%20made%20me%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20genre.%20The%20whole%20scene%20was%20hot%20and%20I%20think%20I%20discovered%20Hip%20Hop%20at%20the%20right%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Moko%20recalls%20how%20he%20was%20a%20timid%20and%20shy%20person%20who%20was%20scared%20to%20talk%20in%20front%20of%20people.%20Hip%20Hop%20helped%20him%20find%20his%20voice.%20%E2%80%9CHip%20Hop%20was%20like%20a%20second%20father%20to%20me.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20express%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoko%20was%2014%20when%20he%20wrote%20his%20first%20song%20and%20two%20years%20later%20composed%20and%20recorded%20his%20first%20song%20%E2%80%98Listen%20to%20Your%20Heart%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone%20at%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20song%20I%20recorded%20was%20on%20a%20phone.%20I%20transferred%20the%20audio%20to%20a%20computer%20and%20used%20a%20software%20called%20Virtual%20DJ%20where%20I%20had%20to%20sync%20the%20music%20and%20audio%20without%20any%20mixing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20writing%20songs%20and%20making%20music%2C%20Moko%20was%20also%20a%20good%20student.%20After%20high%20school%2C%20he%20got%20into%20the%20prestigious%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.t